==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kava
<hw>Ka"va</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Polynesian.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A species of <gen>Macropiper</gen>
(<spn>Macropiper methysticum</spn>), the long pepper, from the root of
which an intoxicating beverage is made by the Polynesians, by a process
of mastication; also, the beverage itself.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>kawa</asp>, <asp>kava</asp>, and <asp>ava</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kavass</ent>⟦br⟧
